REPORT ZINTERNAL_HASHINGTABLE18.

*[[  Tech_54_0641  ]].

*Creating the Structure.
TYPES : BEGIN OF ls_data,
        pro_id(3) TYPE N,
        pro_name TYPE string,
        pro_amount(8) TYPE N,
        pro_date TYPE D,
        END OF ls_data.

*Declaring the Internal Table.
DATA it_data TYPE HASHED TABLE OF ls_data WITH UNIQUE KEY pro_id .
DATA wa TYPE ls_data.

*Inserting the Values into Hashing Table.
wa-pro_id = '8001'.
wa-pro_name = 'MOOHAN'.
wa-pro_amount = '987602'.
wa-pro_date = sy-datum.
INSERT wa INTO TABLE it_data.
